data.description: Renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, Boasting a perfect blend of Modern Luxury and Functionality. Nestled in a Prime Location close to the Beach, Shopping, and some of the best restaurants. This Home has been tastefully Redone, from the Floors to the Kitchen. The Kitchen showcases level 4 granite and Top-of-the-line Appliances. The main bathroom has a Jacuzzi! This smart home is equipped with cutting-edge technology and also the energy efficiency of a solar-powered home, contributing to both sustainability and cost savings. Your peace of mind is assured with hurricane protection provided by impact windows and doors throughout the home. This feature not only enhances safety but also reduces insurance costs. The HUGE backyard is a true Entertainer's Paradise. The Beautifully Landscaped yard is designed for hosting gatherings and celebrations. A Gazebo and Firepit provide the perfect setting for Outdoor Entertaining. Whether you're hosting a Barbecue or simply enjoying a Quiet evening under the Stars, this backyard is a haven for Relaxation and Enjoyment. PLENTY OF ROOM FOR A POOL! Incredible Potential for this Property as a High-End Airbnb or Student Housing.
